                     <ODB_PROPERTY_LIST>
                        <COMMENT>Formula Text. Fast Formula source code for the template. NULL is allowed for templates that only provide prompt guidance in ADDITIONAL_PROMPT_TEXT without a starter code body.</COMMENT>
                     </ODB_PROPERTY_LIST>
